{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":372,"text":"I think we're all aware"},{"time":2085,"text":"that the world today is full of problems."},{"time":5058,"text":"We've been hearing them"},{"time":7153,"text":"today and yesterday and every day for decades."},{"time":11443,"text":"Serious problems, big problems, pressing problems."},{"time":15487,"text":"Poor nutrition, access to water,"},{"time":18843,"text":"climate change, deforestation,"},{"time":21880,"text":"lack of skills, insecurity, not enough food,"},{"time":25124,"text":"not enough healthcare, pollution."},{"time":28100,"text":"There's problem after problem,"},{"time":29845,"text":"and I think what really separates this time"},{"time":32376,"text":"from any time I can remember in my brief time"},{"time":36500,"text":"on Earth is the awareness of these problems."},{"time":38935,"text":"We're all very aware."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41501,"text":"Why are we having so much trouble"},{"time":43529,"text":"dealing with these problems?"},{"time":45360,"text":"That's the question I've been struggling with,"},{"time":48400,"text":"coming from my very different perspective."},{"time":52569,"text":"I'm not a social problem guy."},{"time":55652,"text":"I'm a guy that works with business,"},{"time":58414,"text":"helps business make money."},{"time":61704,"text":"God forbid."},{"time":64938,"text":"So why are we having so many problems"},{"time":67992,"text":"with these social problems,"},{"time":71135,"text":"and really is there any role for business,"},{"time":73192,"text":"and if so, what is that role?"},{"time":76725,"text":"I think that in order to address that question,"},{"time":79584,"text":"we have to step back and think about"},{"time":83450,"text":"how we've understood and pondered"},{"time":87105,"text":"both the problems and the solutions"},{"time":89103,"text":"to these great social challenges that we face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93267,"text":"Now, I think many have seen business"},{"time":96101,"text":"as the problem, or at least one of the problems,"},{"time":98976,"text":"in many of the social challenges we face."},{"time":101728,"text":"You know, think of the fast food industry,"},{"time":103134,"text":"the drug industry, the banking industry."},{"time":105109,"text":"You know, this is a low point"},{"time":107288,"text":"in the respect for business."},{"time":110279,"text":"Business is not seen as the solution."},{"time":111989,"text":"It's seen as the problem now, for most people."},{"time":115730,"text":"And rightly so, in many cases."},{"time":117704,"text":"There's a lot of bad actors out there"},{"time":119983,"text":"that have done the wrong thing,"},{"time":122160,"text":"that actually have made the problem worse."},{"time":123961,"text":"So this perspective is perhaps justified."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127424,"text":"How have we tended to see the solutions"},{"time":130014,"text":"to these social problems,"},{"time":132350,"text":"these many issues that we face in society?"},{"time":135512,"text":"Well, we've tended to see the solutions"},{"time":137144,"text":"in terms of NGOs,"},{"time":139296,"text":"in terms of government,"},{"time":141302,"text":"in terms of philanthropy."},{"time":143439,"text":"Indeed, the kind of unique organizational entity"},{"time":145873,"text":"of this age is this tremendous rise of NGOs"},{"time":150630,"text":"and social organizations."},{"time":153136,"text":"This is a unique, new organizational form"},{"time":155960,"text":"that we've seen grown up."},{"time":157153,"text":"Enormous innovation, enormous energy,"},{"time":160560,"text":"enormous talent now has been mobilized"},{"time":163295,"text":"through this structure"},{"time":165415,"text":"to try to deal with all of these challenges."},{"time":170268,"text":"And many of us here are deeply involved in that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174525,"text":"I'm a business school professor,"},{"time":176034,"text":"but I've actually founded, I think, now, four nonprofits."},{"time":180049,"text":"Whenever I got interested and became aware"},{"time":182938,"text":"of a societal problem, that was what I did,"},{"time":185998,"text":"form a nonprofit."},{"time":187876,"text":"That was the way we've thought about how to deal"},{"time":190939,"text":"with these issues."},{"time":191948,"text":"Even a business school professor has thought about it that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196400,"text":"But I think at this moment,"},{"time":198235,"text":"we've been at this for quite a while."},{"time":201004,"text":"We've been aware of these problems for decades."},{"time":203856,"text":"We have decades of experience"},{"time":205766,"text":"with our NGOs and with our government entities,"},{"time":210091,"text":"and there's an awkward reality."},{"time":211920,"text":"The awkward reality is we're not making"},{"time":213862,"text":"fast enough progress."},{"time":216446,"text":"We're not winning."},{"time":219170,"text":"These problems still seem very daunting"},{"time":221254,"text":"and very intractable,"},{"time":222460,"text":"and any solutions we're achieving"},{"time":225160,"text":"are small solutions."},{"time":227100,"text":"We're making incremental progress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230982,"text":"What's the fundamental problem we have"},{"time":233704,"text":"in dealing with these social problems?"},{"time":236782,"text":"If we cut all the complexity away,"},{"time":240814,"text":"we have the problem of scale."},{"time":244193,"text":"We can't scale."},{"time":247304,"text":"We can make progress. We can show benefits."},{"time":250231,"text":"We can show results. We can make things better."},{"time":253559,"text":"We're helping. We're doing better. We're doing good."},{"time":257837,"text":"We can't scale."},{"time":260191,"text":"We can't make a large-scale impact on these problems."},{"time":265157,"text":"Why is that?"},{"time":266991,"text":"Because we don't have the resources."},{"time":270581,"text":"And that's really clear now."},{"time":272292,"text":"And that's clearer now than it's been for decades."},{"time":275174,"text":"There's simply not enough money"},{"time":278726,"text":"to deal with any of these problems at scale"},{"time":282117,"text":"using the current model."},{"time":284442,"text":"There's not enough tax revenue,"},{"time":287512,"text":"there's not enough philanthropic donations,"},{"time":291558,"text":"to deal with these problems the way we're dealing with them now."},{"time":294006,"text":"We've got to confront that reality."},{"time":299171,"text":"And the scarcity of resources"},{"time":302230,"text":"for dealing with these problems is only growing,"},{"time":306257,"text":"certainly in the advanced world today,"},{"time":309807,"text":"with all the fiscal problems we face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314186,"text":"So if it's fundamentally a resource problem,"},{"time":318431,"text":"where are the resources in society?"},{"time":322476,"text":"How are those resources really created,"},{"time":324861,"text":"the resources we're going to need to deal"},{"time":326568,"text":"with all these societal challenges?"},{"time":330208,"text":"Well there, I think the answer is very clear:"},{"time":333324,"text":"They're in business."},{"time":337010,"text":"All wealth is actually created by business."},{"time":342621,"text":"Business creates wealth"},{"time":345347,"text":"when it meets needs at a profit."},{"time":350393,"text":"That's how all wealth is created."},{"time":352857,"text":"It's meeting needs at a profit"},{"time":355230,"text":"that leads to taxes"},{"time":357642,"text":"and that leads to incomes"},{"time":359311,"text":"and that leads to charitable donations."},{"time":361578,"text":"That's where all the resources come from."},{"time":364829,"text":"Only business can actually create resources."},{"time":367287,"text":"Other institutions can utilize them"},{"time":369241,"text":"to do important work,"},{"time":370466,"text":"but only business can create them."},{"time":373650,"text":"And business creates them"},{"time":375171,"text":"when it's able to meet a need at a profit."},{"time":383049,"text":"The resources are overwhelmingly"},{"time":386433,"text":"generated by business."},{"time":388322,"text":"The question then is, how do we tap into this?"},{"time":393625,"text":"How do we tap into this?"},{"time":396000,"text":"Business generates those resources"},{"time":398947,"text":"when it makes a profit."},{"time":403616,"text":"That profit is that small difference"},{"time":406990,"text":"between the price and the cost it takes to produce"},{"time":411836,"text":"whatever solution business has created"},{"time":414153,"text":"to whatever problem they're trying to solve."},{"time":417376,"text":"But that profit is the magic."},{"time":424136,"text":"Why? Because that profit allows whatever solution"},{"time":428890,"text":"we've created"},{"time":431109,"text":"to be infinitely scalable."},{"time":435299,"text":"Because if we can make a profit,"},{"time":437900,"text":"we can do it for 10, 100, a million,"},{"time":441424,"text":"100 million, a billion."},{"time":444716,"text":"The solution becomes self-sustaining."},{"time":449436,"text":"That's what business does"},{"time":452035,"text":"when it makes a profit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455645,"text":"Now what does this all have to do"},{"time":458029,"text":"with social problems?"},{"time":461097,"text":"Well, one line of thinking is, let's take this profit"},{"time":464379,"text":"and redeploy it into social problems."},{"time":469928,"text":"Business should give more."},{"time":471194,"text":"Business should be more responsible."},{"time":472618,"text":"And that's been the path that we've been on"},{"time":475068,"text":"in business."},{"time":477754,"text":"But again, this path that we've been on"},{"time":479618,"text":"is not getting us where we need to go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483958,"text":"Now, I started out as a strategy professor,"},{"time":487106,"text":"and I'm still a strategy professor."},{"time":488612,"text":"I'm proud of that."},{"time":489971,"text":"But I've also, over the years,"},{"time":491497,"text":"worked more and more on social issues."},{"time":494153,"text":"I've worked on healthcare, the environment,"},{"time":497420,"text":"economic development, reducing poverty,"},{"time":500992,"text":"and as I worked more and more in the social field,"},{"time":505337,"text":"I started seeing something"},{"time":506899,"text":"that had a profound impact on me"},{"time":510169,"text":"and my whole life, in a way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513755,"text":"The conventional wisdom in economics"},{"time":517544,"text":"and the view in business has historically been"},{"time":521412,"text":"that actually, there's a tradeoff"},{"time":525369,"text":"between social performance and economic performance."},{"time":530377,"text":"The conventional wisdom has been"},{"time":531861,"text":"that business actually makes a profit"},{"time":534931,"text":"by causing a social problem."},{"time":536724,"text":"The classic example is pollution."},{"time":538906,"text":"If business pollutes, it makes more money"},{"time":541682,"text":"than if it tried to reduce that pollution."},{"time":546323,"text":"Reducing pollution is expensive,"},{"time":548214,"text":"therefore businesses don't want to do it."},{"time":553697,"text":"It's profitable to have an unsafe working environment."},{"time":556642,"text":"It's too expensive to have a safe working environment,"},{"time":559380,"text":"therefore business makes more money"},{"time":560686,"text":"if they don't have a safe working environment."},{"time":562526,"text":"That's been the conventional wisdom."},{"time":566023,"text":"A lot of companies have fallen into that conventional wisdom."},{"time":568836,"text":"They resisted environmental improvement."},{"time":571379,"text":"They resisted workplace improvement."},{"time":576813,"text":"That thinking has led to, I think,"},{"time":580359,"text":"much of the behavior"},{"time":581879,"text":"that we have come to criticize in business,"},{"time":583815,"text":"that I come to criticize in business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586335,"text":"But the more deeply I got into all these social issues,"},{"time":589868,"text":"one after another,"},{"time":592880,"text":"and actually, the more I tried to address them"},{"time":595326,"text":"myself, personally, in a few cases,"},{"time":597442,"text":"through nonprofits that I was involved with,"},{"time":600171,"text":"the more I found actually that the reality"},{"time":603109,"text":"is the opposite."},{"time":605643,"text":"Business does not profit"},{"time":606889,"text":"from causing social problems,"},{"time":608591,"text":"actually not in any fundamental sense."},{"time":612965,"text":"That's a very simplistic view."},{"time":615158,"text":"The deeper we get into these issues,"},{"time":617866,"text":"the more we start to understand"},{"time":619711,"text":"that actually business profits"},{"time":621612,"text":"from solving from social problems."},{"time":623608,"text":"That's where the real profit comes."},{"time":626152,"text":"Let's take pollution."},{"time":628993,"text":"We've learned today that actually"},{"time":631209,"text":"reducing pollution and emissions"},{"time":633616,"text":"is generating profit."},{"time":637122,"text":"It saves money."},{"time":639190,"text":"It makes the business more productive and efficient."},{"time":640888,"text":"It doesn't waste resources."},{"time":642285,"text":"Having a safer working environment actually,"},{"time":644928,"text":"and avoiding accidents,"},{"time":646416,"text":"it makes the business more profitable,"},{"time":647788,"text":"because it's a sign of good processes."},{"time":650996,"text":"Accidents are expensive and costly."},{"time":655027,"text":"Issue by issue by issue, we start to learn"},{"time":657631,"text":"that actually there's no trade-off"},{"time":660597,"text":"between social progress"},{"time":664193,"text":"and economic efficiency"},{"time":667194,"text":"in any fundamental sense."},{"time":669287,"text":"Another issue is health."},{"time":670646,"text":"I mean, what we've found is actually"},{"time":673215,"text":"health of employees is something"},{"time":675097,"text":"that business should treasure,"},{"time":676490,"text":"because that health allows those employees"},{"time":678818,"text":"to be more productive and come to work"},{"time":680227,"text":"and not be absent."},{"time":682543,"text":"The deeper work, the new work, the new thinking"},{"time":685967,"text":"on the interface between business and social problems"},{"time":690151,"text":"is actually showing that there's a fundamental,"},{"time":693069,"text":"deep synergy,"},{"time":694988,"text":"particularly if you're not thinking in the very short run."},{"time":698916,"text":"In the very short run, you can sometimes"},{"time":700754,"text":"fool yourself into thinking"},{"time":702855,"text":"that there's fundamentally opposing goals,"},{"time":705150,"text":"but in the long run, ultimately, we're learning"},{"time":707963,"text":"in field after field that this is simply not true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712159,"text":"So how could we tap into"},{"time":715449,"text":"the power of business"},{"time":718171,"text":"to address the fundamental problems"},{"time":720374,"text":"that we face?"},{"time":722807,"text":"Imagine if we could do that, because if we could do it,"},{"time":725407,"text":"we could scale."},{"time":727447,"text":"We could tap into this enormous resource pool"},{"time":729856,"text":"and this organizational capacity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732754,"text":"And guess what? That's happening now, finally,"},{"time":738244,"text":"partly because of people like you"},{"time":742257,"text":"who have raised these issues now"},{"time":744205,"text":"for year after year and decade after decade."},{"time":747320,"text":"We see organizations like Dow Chemical"},{"time":749728,"text":"leading the revolution away from trans fat"},{"time":751646,"text":"and saturated fat with innovative new products."},{"time":754778,"text":"This is an example of Jain Irrigation."},{"time":756731,"text":"This is a company that's brought drip irrigation technology"},{"time":759282,"text":"to thousands and millions of farmers,"},{"time":761951,"text":"reducing substantially the use of water."},{"time":765002,"text":"We see companies like the Brazilian forestry company Fibria"},{"time":768323,"text":"that's figured out how to avoid"},{"time":769806,"text":"tearing down old growth forest"},{"time":771685,"text":"and using eucalyptus and getting much more yield"},{"time":774461,"text":"per hectare of pulp"},{"time":776451,"text":"and making much more paper than you could make"},{"time":778419,"text":"by cutting down those old trees."},{"time":780528,"text":"You see companies like Cisco that are training"},{"time":783408,"text":"so far four million people in I.T. skills"},{"time":787564,"text":"to actually, yes, be responsible,"},{"time":789507,"text":"but help expand the opportunity"},{"time":791938,"text":"to disseminate I.T. technology"},{"time":794211,"text":"and grow the whole business."},{"time":795513,"text":"There's a fundamental opportunity for business today"},{"time":800134,"text":"to impact and address these social problems,"},{"time":804190,"text":"and this opportunity"},{"time":805514,"text":"is the largest business opportunity"},{"time":808782,"text":"we see in business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812448,"text":"And the question is, how can we get business"},{"time":814654,"text":"thinking to adapt this issue of shared value?"},{"time":818082,"text":"This is what I call shared value:"},{"time":819891,"text":"addressing a social issue with a business model."},{"time":823646,"text":"That's shared value."},{"time":825570,"text":"Shared value is capitalism,"},{"time":827399,"text":"but it's a higher kind of capitalism."},{"time":829961,"text":"It's capitalism as it was ultimately meant to be,"},{"time":833321,"text":"meeting important needs,"},{"time":836734,"text":"not incrementally competing for"},{"time":839557,"text":"trivial differences in product attributes"},{"time":842820,"text":"and market share."},{"time":844553,"text":"Shared value is when we can create social value"},{"time":846772,"text":"and economic value simultaneously."},{"time":849375,"text":"It's finding those opportunities"},{"time":851885,"text":"that will unleash the greatest possibility we have"},{"time":854950,"text":"to actually address these social problems"},{"time":856941,"text":"because we can scale."},{"time":858974,"text":"We can address shared value at multiple levels."},{"time":862530,"text":"It's real. It's happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":865695,"text":"But in order to get this solution working,"},{"time":868588,"text":"we have to now change how business sees itself,"},{"time":872716,"text":"and this is thankfully underway."},{"time":875230,"text":"Businesses got trapped into the conventional wisdom"},{"time":878706,"text":"that they shouldn't worry about social problems,"},{"time":880554,"text":"that this was sort of something on the side,"},{"time":882596,"text":"that somebody else was doing it."},{"time":885177,"text":"We're now seeing companies"},{"time":886753,"text":"embrace this idea."},{"time":889229,"text":"But we also have to recognize business"},{"time":891418,"text":"is not going to do this as effectively"},{"time":894162,"text":"as if we have NGOs and government"},{"time":896022,"text":"working in partnership with business."},{"time":899053,"text":"The new NGOs that are really moving the needle"},{"time":902061,"text":"are the ones that have found these partnerships,"},{"time":904244,"text":"that have found these ways to collaborate."},{"time":906061,"text":"The governments that are making the most progress"},{"time":908534,"text":"are the governments that have found ways"},{"time":910148,"text":"to enable shared value in business"},{"time":913799,"text":"rather than see government as the only player"},{"time":916920,"text":"that has to call the shots."},{"time":919934,"text":"And government has many ways in which it could impact"},{"time":922406,"text":"the willingness and the ability of companies"},{"time":924720,"text":"to compete in this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926714,"text":"I think if we can get business seeing itself differently,"},{"time":929663,"text":"and if we can get others seeing business differently,"},{"time":932206,"text":"we can change the world."},{"time":935011,"text":"I know it. I'm seeing it."},{"time":938216,"text":"I'm feeling it."},{"time":940166,"text":"Young people, I think,"},{"time":941861,"text":"my Harvard Business School students, are getting it."},{"time":945041,"text":"If we can break down this sort of divide,"},{"time":949363,"text":"this unease, this tension,"},{"time":952373,"text":"this sense that we're not"},{"time":954303,"text":"fundamentally collaborating here"},{"time":956543,"text":"in driving these social problems,"},{"time":958893,"text":"we can break this down,"},{"time":960997,"text":"and we finally, I think,"},{"time":962997,"text":"can have solutions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":965629,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968429,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}